bio: Sarah has over 10 years of experience in luxury real estate markets across the region, specializing in high-end properties and executive homes.
Michael specializes in commercial properties and has helped numerous businesses find their perfect location over his 8-year career.
Jennifer is our residential specialist with extensive knowledge of the suburban markets and school districts.
David has a background in construction and provides valuable insights into property conditions and renovation potential.
Emma specializes in helping first-time homebuyers navigate the purchasing process with confidence.
James has unparalleled knowledge of the downtown market and specializes in urban properties and condominiums.
Lisa specializes in luxury vacation properties and second homes in resort communities.
Robert has extensive experience in property management and investment properties, helping investors maximize their returns.
Amanda specializes in historic homes and properties with unique character, bringing a passion for preservation to her work.
Thomas has a background in finance and specializes in helping clients understand the investment aspects of real estate.
